  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We ensure the default index doesn't show up in ui state, but instead gets applied in getWidgetSearchParameters so that the default index case doesn't need to be handled in routing (as most the default state of any widget doesn't show up in the url). If we'd have that in ui state, you'd either need to remove it in stateToRoute or have an update of the URL on first load of the page.",
